title: Lunar Crater Simulation
description: This forward simulation maps the cratering pattern on the moon's surface, spanning 2 billion years from the beginning of time.

title: Modeling the Atmospheres of Brown Dwarfs
description: Using UCDMCMC, we model the atmoshperes of brown dwarfs using various models such as elfowl, and btsettle

title: Nutrition Data Visualization
description: Whole Foods is the Healthiest Store Across Multiple Metrics. We analyzed a dataset with nutritional info on many stores

title: Total Strain on Workers: Data Vizualization
description: This project showcases how the same data can be used to show opposite trends. Here I am vizulaizing the total strain on workers, and I use multiple metrics such as the old-age dependency ratio, as well as the total-dependency ratio.

title: Brown Dwarf Identification Model
description: We use gaussian resampling to create synthetic spectra and add it to our sample of brown dwarfs. We made a binary machine learning model to identify brown dwarfs.

title: Catalog of Galaxies
description: We created a catalog of galaxies, here we have the non interacting objects.
